Oracle PL/SQL-
select * from dual
where rownum < 'here put the number of rows to fetch'

+ If you need select max 1 salary

    select salary from employee
    where rownum < 2
    order by salary desc

+ If you need to select mininum salary of employee, 
    select salary from employee
    where rownum < 2
    order by salary asc

